The paper deals with object detection in images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of transfer learning and domain adaptation techniques also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of the methodology to fashion detection and Cityscapes datasets indicates a potential interest in multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
